“The International Journal of Psycho-Analysis“ takes
the place for English speaking readers of the Inter—
nationale Zeitsclmlf'tj'z'lr Rsychocmalyse and Image, which

International Psycho-Analytical Association, of which it is,
together with the Zeitschrift and Imago, the Ofﬁcial Organ.

The Journal will be issued quarterly, the four parts
constituting & volume of between 400 and 500 pages. It
